column5: Looking for a good spot to take my little girl shore fishing for some perch. Looking to get out tomorrow any help would be appreciated thank you for any help
Thanks for the info Cudz my little girl is pumped now for some perch action
Drove by this morning. They know have the gates chained.
Are all the boats gone from the marina yet?

Was a great day landed 2 jumbos my little girl landed her first baby bass ever. Lots of people out today saw many jumbos being cought. The sun was out and the winds were down great day to be out with the kids
Sounds like a great day with your daughter Jose!  Congratulations on the jumbos and your little fishing partner's first fish!
